			<div class="content" id="post-content-3962836">
									

<p>I liked it.<br />
Nobody ever talks about HOW cognitohazard checks work.<br />
And this actually makes sense. It's not a failed attempt.<br />
The dialogue to me seemed like it was professional and rapid-succession like it should be, not a bare skeleton.<br />
But I guess I'm not experienced here like the other people. I only got the GOI references, so I'm a little shallow into it still.<br />
I liked it though.</p>

